見到光復香港，我哋一齊發聲，令美國人知道香港及世界的民主都需要共和黨政府。<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n[如何參與 #HKforTrump]<br />\n<br />\n我們希望大家拍攝影片並在片中說出你們支持Trump的理由，可使用中文或英文，我們最後會加上字幕。拍片時，亦可以舉起支持Trump既標語，可選擇露樣或蒙面。<br />\n<br />\n完成後，各位可將影片傳送至<br />\nhkfortrump@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n或Telegram :<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKforTrump\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKforTrump&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=c0789f44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKforTrump</a><br />\n<br />\n大家亦可以自己放上social media再標記 #hkfortrump<br />\n<br />\n如果大家諗唔到講咩，以下係參考對白：<br />\n<br />\nThank President Trump for supporting Hong Kong<br />\n<br />\n2020 Vote Trump!<br />\n<br />\nFreedom won't come back if you give it away.<br />\n<br />\nChina is asshole!<br />\n<br />\nMake the world great again<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------<br />\n順便支持埋我哋 獨角獸 Indicorn Union 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/Indicorn.union/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2FIndicorn.union%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KigKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=c966c2bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/Indicorn.union/</a>"},{"pid":"eedb245644027b22d11bd911d34cc89efb72cf01","tid":2262044,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:05:48.000Z","msg":"咁多負<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過好似趕唔切<br />\n不如下個節日著紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}